snippet.title: Lawful Masses with Leonard French
snippet.description: I'm a tinkerer, programmer, and lawyer. I try to talk about interesting topics related to law and technology. Plus, you'll find various videos that I enjoy sharing. I love to hear your comments, questions, and suggestions, and try to answer whenever I can.
